title: Iran installs cameras to ID women breaking dress code
description: Iranian authorities are to use cameras in public places to identify women who violate the country's hijab law, state media reported.

title: Glut of cheap Ukrainian grain sparks farmers' protests
description: Farmers in central and eastern Europe protested this week against the impact of cheap Ukrainian grain imports, which have undercut domestic prices and hit the sales of local producers.

title: Italian tourist killed in Israel car-ramming attack
description: An Italian tourist was killed and seven people wounded in a car-ramming attack in the Israeli city of Tel Aviv on Friday evening.

title: China military rehearses 'encircling' Taiwan after US Speaker visit
description:

title: Zelensky shares Iftar with Muslim soldiers in 'new tradition of respect'
description: Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky shared Iftar with Ukrainian Muslim soldiers observing Ramadan on Friday, in what he said would become an annual "new tradition of respect."
